<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>You're on the Toaster waitlist</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#0e0f0f;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;color:#d4d6d6;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background:#0e0f0f;padding:40px 20px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:520px;">

            <%# Logo %>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding-bottom:32px;">
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="background:#f59e0b;border-radius:6px;width:28px;height:28px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;">
                      🍞
                    </td>
                    <td style="padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#f0f2f2;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
                      Toaster
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <%# Headline %>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding-bottom:16px;">
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:#f0f2f2;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">
                  You're on the list.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <%# Body %>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding-bottom:32px;border-bottom:1px solid #252626;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#d4d6d6;">
                  We got your spot saved. Toaster is invite-only while we work closely with a small
                  group of early operators — you'll hear from us when your access opens up.
                </p>
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#d4d6d6;">
                  In the meantime: if you manage a venue and are drowning in booking emails,
                  that's exactly the problem we're solving.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <%# What Toaster does %>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding-top:28px;padding-bottom:32px;border-bottom:1px solid #252626;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4a4d4d;">
                  What Toaster does
                </p>
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1a1a;">
                      <span style="color:#f59e0b;font-weight:bold;margin-right:12px;">—</span>
                      <span style="font-size:12px;color:#d4d6d6;">Reads every booking inquiry the moment it arrives</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1a1a;">
                      <span style="color:#f59e0b;font-weight:bold;margin-right:12px;">—</span>
                      <span style="font-size:12px;color:#d4d6d6;">Extracts date, headcount, budget — organized automatically</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:10px 0;">
                      <span style="color:#f59e0b;font-weight:bold;margin-right:12px;">—</span>
                      <span style="font-size:12px;color:#d4d6d6;">Drafts the reply in your voice — you approve, it sends</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <%# Footer %>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding-top:28px;">
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#4a4d4d;line-height:1.6;">
                  You're receiving this because you signed up at the Toaster waitlist.<br>
                  No spam — just a heads-up when your spot opens.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
